author: Rosie
install_msg:
Thanks for installing songshare! Keep in mind that this Cog interacts with Odesli/Songlink!
This cog does not respect ingored channels or guilds, neither blacklisted/whitelisted users
Use the integrated channel/guild selection instead
name: songshare
short: Share music with every music service
description: Easily share music thanks to universally translated links
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any end user data, but remember that it interacts with the Songlink API.
